==English==

===Noun===
'''Needlework'''

1. the art or process of working with a needle [[esp.]] in [[embroidery]] or [[needlepoint]] .

2. the product of such art or process.

3. the [[occupation]] or [[employment]] of a person skilled in [[embroidery]], [[needlepoint]], ect.

===Synonyms===

1.[[needlecraft]]

